Stream Operations:-

System.out: Output stream
System.in: Input stream
System.err: error stream


Intermediate Operations

filter()
map()
flatMap()
distinct()
sorted()
peek()
limit()
skip()

Terminal Operations

forEach()
forEachOrdered()
toArray()
reduce()
collect()
min()
max()
count()
anyMatch()
allMatch()
noneMatch()
findFirst()
findAny()

Flatmap:- map() is used for transformation only but flatmap is used for both transformation and flattening.
flatMap = map+ Flattening;

Can we reuse stream? No.
@we cannot reuse the streams or traverse the streams multiple times. Any attempt to do so will result in error :
Stream has already been operated on or closed.